== 軍事 ==
{{Main|叙利亚军事}}
武器：前[[蘇聯|蘇聯]]時代研發的坦克、[[自行火炮|自行火炮]]、[[飛毛腿導彈|飛毛腿導彈]]、[[米格-23|米格-23]]（敘利亞的米格-23在2002年曾擊落22架以色列的無人偵察機）。

兵种有陆军，海军，空军和防空部队。现役部队的人数为20万，预备役为160万人。正规职业军人中95%是[[阿萨德家族|阿萨德家族]]所属的[[阿拉维派|阿拉维派]]，而军官中的阿拉维派更是占98%。[[叙利亚共和国卫队|叙利亚共和国卫队]]和第四机械装甲部队是叙利亚的精锐部队，几乎全部由阿拉维派组成，并且都由总统巴沙尔的弟弟[[马赫尔·阿萨德|马赫尔·阿萨德]]亲自领导指挥。这样的组成结构目的是确保军队对总统家族的绝对效忠。至2015年敘利亞政府軍因內戰耗損已由原本的30萬正規軍，降至15萬正規軍。

[[俄罗斯|俄罗斯]]一直是叙利亚最大的武器供应国，叙利亚也是俄羅斯在[[中東|中東]]地區的[[亲俄|唯一重要盟友]]<ref name=SIPRI>{{cite web |title=SIPRI Arms Transfers Database |url=http://armstrade.sipri.org/armstrade/page/values.php |publisher=Stockholm International Peace Research Institute |accessdate=8 September 2011 |archive-date=2015-11-25 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151125105813/http://armstrade.sipri.org/armstrade/page/values.php |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name=Amos>{{cite news|last=Amos|first=Howard|title=News Analysis: Russia Damages Image in Arab Spring|url=http://www.themoscowtimes.com/business/article/news-analysis-russia-damages-image-in-arab-spring/442712.html|accessdate=8 September 2011|newspaper=The Moscow Times|date=26 August 2011|archive-date=2011-12-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20111222175458/http://www.themoscowtimes.com/business/article/news-analysis-russia-damages-image-in-arab-spring/442712.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name=CAST>{{cite web |title=Russian defense industry and arms trade:  facts and figures |url=http://www.cast.ru/files/2011/all-stats_eng_2011_05_12.pdf |publisher=Centre for Analysis of Strategies and Technologies. pp 15 |accessdate=8 September 2011 |archive-date=2011-11-20 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20111120172100/http://www.cast.ru/files/2011/all-stats_eng_2011_05_12.pdf |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name=Meyer>{{cite news |last=Meyer |first=Henry |script-title=en:Assad Ouster Bid May Unleash‘Chaos in Mideast,’Russia Says |url=http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-09-07/assad-ouster-bid-may-unleash-chaos-in-mideast-russia-says.html |accessdate=2011-09-08 |newspaper=Bloomberg |date=2011-09-07 |archive-date=2012-04-27 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120427145004/http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-09-07/assad-ouster-bid-may-unleash-chaos-in-mideast-russia-says.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

